## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of recent data, as some sources are dated and may not reflect the latest research developments. Additionally, the complexity of social influence means that individual experiences can vary widely, and the findings may not be universally applicable. Further research could explore more recent studies and diverse cultural contexts to provide a more comprehensive view.